README -- Describes contents of splash_page_scripts
21 Mar 2025
GEOS-Chem Support Team

This folder contains scripts to generate plots and/or tables for the
GEOS-Chem website splash page.  Several metrics will be generated for
display on the splash page.

Lines of code
-------------

./count_loc.sh:         Counts the number of lines of code in a repository.
                        Requires the "cloc" package.

./display_loc_gcc.sh:   Plots the output from count_loc.sh
                        (for GEOS-Chem Classic)

./display_loc_gchp.sh:  Plots the output from count_loc.sh
                        (for GCHP)